-- Wal-Mart Stores Says It Creates Position for FCPA Compliance
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2012-04-24T17:14:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/wal-mart-stores-says-it-creates-position-for-fcpa-compliance.html
Wal-Mart Stores Inc. (WMT)  said it has
created a new position for global compliance with the U.S.
Foreign Corrupt Practices Act, among other actions to bolster
compliance.   The new position will oversee five compliance directors
based in international markets.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  